{"tid":1212540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大家請注意]下次野餐可以帶呢樣野，一定有用","createTime":"2019-06-12T19:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T07:50:59.000Z","uid":70786,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a4daca3a8be904dd968b067dbce16ea898a70e","tid":1212540,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2017/642/015/4323510246_497947529.310x310.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbu01.alicdn.com%2Fimg%2Fibank%2F2017%2F642%2F015%2F4323510246_497947529.310x310.jpg&h=88e5ceee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係洗面盆，應該人人屋企都有，上次去野餐俾人趕走咗，最衰都係D好攻鼻嘅煙，D死煙剷好鍾意得寸進尺，你俾D煙攻到眼濕口咳佢地就步步進逼，其實係有個解決方法：<br />\n１.用個洗面盆笠住D出煙嘅可疑物。<br />\n２.用預先準備好嘅濕毛巾係個盆邊圍一圈，就可以有效減少百分之九十九臭煙，入面燃燒緊嘅物體仲會因為缺氧而慢慢熄滅。<br />\n尺寸唔使太大，一條毛巾圍到個盆邊就Fit晒！去野餐整到污糟邋遢又可以用嚟洗野<br />\n洗面盆，家居必備良品，欲購從速，以免向隅，各大家品及百貨公司有售<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外再向大家介紹多一款產品，唔講咁多立即去片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=NqaFa2919QA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D1%26v%3DNqaFa2919QA&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=5cde90e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=NqaFa2919QA</a><br />\n係咪好慳水呢？水資源好緊要架我地要環保係咪？有時去野餐冇水好大鑊架嘛<br />\n如果好大煙可以用噴霧噴佢，咁就唔使望天打卦等落雨啦！<br />\n食辣椒辣到阿媽都唔認得咩？<br />\n裝d奶入去用噴霧沖洗表面辣椒素，咁就唔辣架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過小心d奶常溫唔放得耐，變咗就唔好飲用，用嚟沖洗好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二百幾蚊好襟用架，我係2014年Kickstarter第一批backer，用到今時今日都未壞<br />\n平時一個水樽都要百幾蚊啦，買一個aquabot仲好。<br />\n可以係邊度買到呢？<br />\n自己去google Aquabot Water Bottle 壓力噴射水樽<br />\n我有係Log-on見過<br />\n部份香港本地露營用品公司都有入貨<br />\n<br />\nAmazon都有得買架，仲直送香港添！<br />\n不過要留意翻有d色係要6月16，甚至係6月22先有貨！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Lunatec-Aquabot-Pressure-Multi-Purpose-Personal/dp/B00WKWHKNQ/ref=sr_1_12?keywords=aquabot&amp;qid=1560364362&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-12&amp;th=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLunatec-Aquabot-Pressure-Multi-Purpose-Personal%2Fdp%2FB00WKWHKNQ%2Fref%3Dsr_1_12%3Fkeywords%3Daquabot%26qid%3D1560364362%26s%3Dgateway%26sr%3D8-12%26th%3D1&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=3542e213\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Lunatec-Aquabot-Pressure-Multi-Purpose-Personal/dp/B00WKWHKNQ/ref=sr_1_12?keywords=aquabot&amp;qid=1560364362&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-12&amp;th=1</a><br />\n另外各位靚仔靚女埋嚟睇埋嚟揀喇喂，手快有手慢冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a4f97b0dcb76e7ef8b068eb881f651a1645e66","tid":1212540,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:26:22.000Z","msg":"如果覺得有用請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871c2033d0b2a3d011b58f2a1e45afd055125237","tid":1212540,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:29:33.000Z","msg":"記得留個like等多d人睇到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486e475334b84514b604adb07210a7d95373a239","tid":1212540,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:30:16.000Z","msg":"夢遊見到個場得一個<br />\n嗰陣仲諗做乜要洗面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6e2173a11233434ccf8e48c58319e520d5d8b0","tid":1212540,"uid":9924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:30:44.000Z","msg":"唔係話想打擊你<br />\n但係佢射個陣你身邊晚人就會走<br />\n因為唔係人人頂到啲煙<br />\n人一散唔聚集<br />\n狗就一湧而上"},{"pid":"ec1f4d7844ce941b87297ff81a2048a737778010","tid":1212540,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:30:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NqaFa2919QA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNqaFa2919QA&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=a329035c\" target=